e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa07c299ba306b83cd6eb8660657f1cb2cfd3200","tid":1835082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"1月24日 星期五 2000-2200 荔枝角:銀髮族三十晚聲援被囚人士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">荔枝角:銀髮族三十晚聲援被囚人士</span><br />\n日期 : 1月24日 星期五<br />\n時間 : 2000-2200<br />\n地點 : 荔枝角收押所正門大閘外<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對知書</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/82759226_1000578406987650_9171989994472996864_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQlBJvt_-DS3izkgYXmekUHx0zZfJ2u8ts-BrGksHzpgAIeRXys59V5z4XkOkCNadDg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=ae768ed67e8652f764de9470f11062c8&amp;oe=5E9DED02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F82759226_1000578406987650_9171989994472996864_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQlBJvt_-DS3izkgYXmekUHx0zZfJ2u8ts-BrGksHzpgAIeRXys59V5z4XkOkCNadDg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dae768ed67e8652f764de9470f11062c8%26oe%3D5E9DED02&h=08bb3741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【銀髪族年三十晚聲援被囚人士】<br />\n*已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n年三十晚集會要人！希望大家能夠抽時間出席！亦希望我哋嘅聲音同埋歌聲能夠傳到去各位被囚手足的耳中。<br />\n<br />\n🎤出席者（排名不分先後):<br />\n程翔<br />\n伍月蘭 深水埗區區議員<br />\n劉偉聰 Lawrence Lau 深水埗區區議員<br />\n馬屎埔陳伯<br />\n黃衍仁<br />\nStefano Lodola 意大利歌唱家<br />\nPepper Band<br />\n銀髮族一眾發起人<br />\n<br />\n📣銀髮族集會守則，希望能保平安！<br />\n1. 確診武漢肺炎已傳到香港，前來集會必定要戴口罩。<br />\n2. 自備水樽，乾糧，藥油，保暖衣物。<br />\n3. 自行製作文宣品。<br />\n4. 全程Be water。<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年1月24日（五）<br />\n時間：晚上八時至十時<br />\n地點：荔枝角收押所正門外<br />\n<br />\n集會詳情🔎 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/995774120801412/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F845348632510629%2Fposts%2F995774120801412%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=9cf52c7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/995774120801412/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n#撐手足撐到底<br />\n#和勇不分齊上齊落<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\nRef : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silverhairgroup/photos/a.845823422463150/1000578403654317/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilverhairgroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.845823422463150%2F1000578403654317%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=9266f791\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silverhairgroup/photos/a.845823422463150/1000578403654317/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"5b73e3c05dce66fc0b5ede03e332459e5d77e845","tid":1835082,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e823d3d613285bedf19edbb7a4da8b55f833b4","tid":1835082,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:03:18.000Z","msg":"help push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c36a7ae72b25334d84b95baaefb7f07ea4fa12","tid":1835082,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9a35fc983366e3056842196a06f0bb4e34e902","tid":1835082,"uid":8732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:17:15.000Z","msg":"今晚要人！！"},{"pid":"7b8265224bc187af5ab5b7c2cd3eccdfc198e9e2","tid":1835082,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/